lyrics:
You may push me around
But you cannot win
You may throw me down
But I'll rise again
The more you say
The more I defy you
So get out of my face – Oh Yeah!

Chorus:
You cannot stop us
You cannot bring us down
Never give up
We go on and on!
You'll never break us
Never bring us down
We are alive!

The wind blows
I'll lean into the wind
My anger grows
I'll use it to win
The more you say
The more I defy you
So get out of my way – Oh Yeah

Bridge:
All my will
All my strength
Rip it out
Start again

Chorus

Bridge

Can you leave it all behind?
Can you leave it all behind?
Cause you can't go back
You can't go back

Chorus
